/* eslint-disable max-len */
const React = require('react');
const Head = require('react-declarative-head');
const PropTypes = require('prop-types');
 
/* eslint-disable nordic/no-style-tags */
// Head's UP! Here we are using the minified versions of our css files
// We need them to be inline, that's why we want to minify them so save as much bundle size as possible
// If you want to make changes to them, please see files ./styles/mobile.css or ./styles/desktop.css,
// apply changes there, minify them and then paste them here.
const namespace = 'ml-labs-logo';
const Lab = (props) => {
  const { labUrl, melilab, isMobile } = props;
 
  return (
    <a className={namespace} href={labUrl}>{melilab}
      <Head>
        <style>{ isMobile
          ? '.ml-labs-logo{position:absolute;top:5px;left:35px;margin-top:17px;padding:0 6px;background:#00008b;border-radius:5px;color:#fff!important;font-size:12px;z-index:1;}'
          : '.ml-labs-logo{background-repeat:no-repeat;margin:0;position:absolute;top:5px;left:125px;text-indent:24px;padding-top:26px;width:33px;height:43px;background-image:url(https://http2.mlstatic.com/resources/frontend/commons-frontend/melilab/tube.png);z-index:1;}'}
        </style>
      </Head>
    </a>
  );
};
 
Lab.propTypes = {
  melilab: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  labUrl: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  isMobile: PropTypes.bool,
};
 
Lab.defaultProps = {
  isMobile: false,
};
 
module.exports = Lab;
